title: LOHAS LED lighting factory
description:
LOHAS LED is a leading lighting factory founded in 2003, with over 20 years of experience in LED lighting industry. Located in Zhongshan city, LOHAS LED covers an factory area of over 5,000 m² and operates 12 production lines for hundreds of LED lighting products. With a monthly production capacity of 1,000,000 pieces LED products, we provide high-quality LED lights to global customers in 120+ countries, and gain great reputation from customers. Offering RTS/OEM/ODM services and worldwide certifications, which is allowing us to fulfill and achieve client’s custom design and special requirements.
Healthy and sustainable lifestyle is highly recommended in LOHAS LED. We are engaging to develop and research the innovative LED lighting products all the time.
